<plot>A security guard working the graveyard shift falls asleep while on duty. When he wakes up, he sees his own body on one of the CCTV monitors lying prostrate on the floor in a chamber. Unsure if he is asleep or awake he goes to investigate, making his way deep into the bowels of the industrial complex where he encounters an intruder that ends up killing him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?396578</url></doc>
